hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Protection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AllowInsertingColumns</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
